{"tid":1007083,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[年度回帶] 拜年請鎖自己房門/保管重要物品","createTime":"2019-02-03T13:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T13:44:14.000Z","uid":70507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c17df416c466f28d46354d1f3340db439f9d6ba9","tid":1007083,"uid":70507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#1 R18A1 &bull; 11 個月前<br />\n年年都發生既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d老豆老母死要面堅持送話咩新年流流大方d啦<br />\n亦有d仆街親戚各種惡行<br />\n呢d事好多時各位巴絲打返工返學期間發生<br />\n因為自己唔係屋企又控制唔到<br />\n返到屋企先知就已經太遲<br />\n之後就同老豆/老母嘈又冇用<br />\n所以提醒各位巴絲打年三十夜前準備好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇自己房既巴絲打:<br />\n整條list出黎寫底邊d重要物品係唔可以拎同送<br />\n又或者盡可能收埋佢地同標示出重要物品價值<br />\n記住print埋出黎貼係唔同角落以免親戚睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n至於有自己房既巴絲打:<br />\n請鎖好門窗以免親戚既小朋友入房<br />\n過住經驗係小朋友見到鐘意/有興趣既野就拎黎玩<br />\n之後到走果陣個小朋友唔肯放手唔肯走<br />\n<br />\n最難搞就係老豆老母見小朋友鐘意就當面話送俾佢<br />\n你老豆老母就好可能話<br />\n&rdquo;你拎去玩啦 唔駛客氣&rdquo;<br />\n同返你講&ldquo;你俾佢啦，你做大既讓下啲細嫁啦&rdquo;<br />\n呢個自己講極又唔得既時侯就用老豆老母最貴重既野送比親戚<br />\n老母既就用佢當年d嫁妝，佢好鐘意既手包之類<br />\n老豆既就陳年紅酒之類<br />\n上年有好多例子，大家可以參考一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個新年幾多人比親戚整爛野/被送禮比表弟妹？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/99313/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/99313/page/1</a><br />\n最後預祝大家新年快樂，出入平安</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今日台仔PTT有篇未過年已經有人俾親戚細倒瀉成碗湯落部switch度直接報銷  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完我都即刻收番部switch入房先 <br />\n各位巴打小心啦 一時心軟出左事無仇報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年既post<br />\n [溫馨提示]拜年請鎖自己房門/保管重要物品 | LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/556313\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/556313</a>"},{"pid":"4e9d91b7a37a567d339debc377abbd50af65d26c","tid":1007083,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:31:16.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"242492f1680c5c406a3e62ddf0482c2ef0dd395a","tid":1007083,"uid":70507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZMEhsb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZMEhsb.jpg&h=1c07492b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d442d628373399cfef7631066ebdf79015410ea","tid":1007083,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:33:58.000Z","msg":"已經擺曬入迷你倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 以前試過瀨野"},{"pid":"802123fd7ea9b03f4cb865c5229c0cdd0c5428d7","tid":1007083,"uid":70507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"1個月前巴打慘劇 BB都唔可以放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n喇叭單元俾親戚個bb 禁爆咗<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/cbxNtS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/cbxNtS</a><br />\n<br />\n#7 7ha7ha 2018年12月23日 <br />\n60k 一對，2手買，冇單"},{"pid":"10924d127592fcec5388899cd6d64cc201c11ec3","tid":1007083,"uid":70507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:44:14.000Z","msg":"蝗仔細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote>#30意色樓 &bull; 11mo<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇左部3ds<br />\nDetails<br />\n個蝗童入左我房拎黎玩 順手拎走埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好彩部野壞壞地 當跌左</blockquote>"}]}